== Iɣerfan ==
Deg Ugafa n Tefriqt, imezdaɣen inaṣliyen d [[Imaziɣen]], d nutni  i d amur ameqqṛan deg yimezdaɣen n [[Tamazɣa|Tmazɣa]], xas ma yella aṭas deg-sen ass-a i yettmeslayen [[taɛrabt]] neɣ [[Tafrensist|Tafṛansist]]. Imaziɣen gan-d tilas i wakal d ameqqṛan, yewwet-d seg umda n [[Isiwan]], deg Umalu n [[Maṣer|Maṣeṛ]] almi d [[Targa Zewwaɣen]] d [[Muriṭanya]], ɣef yiri n ugaraw Atlasi neɣ adrar n watlas. 

Akal n Yimaziɣen, seg wakken meqqeṛ yewweḍ ɣer tlemmast n Tefriqt. D [[Imuhaɣ]] neɣ Imucaɣ i d aɣref n Yimaziɣen i ilan akal meqqren akk gar iɣerfan imaziɣen-nniḍen, xas akken ur gtin ara. Akal-nsen d [[Aneẓruf]] (Idurar n Tasili, n Ayer di [[Nijir]], atg.).

